Rating: 3
We make this all summer long; grill till nice grill marks but still barely tender (we like a fimer texture; remove from grill, sprinkle with parmesan or asiago and a little balsamic while piping hot; THEN let cool. Later one can cut up and add the basil, or grab out of the fridge the "boats" as an on- the-run snack food.

